---
// Modules Component
---
<!-- Modules Showcase Section -->
    <section id="modules" class="reveal">
        <div class="section-header">
            <h2>Automated Safety Workflows</h2>
            <p>Ditch paper checklists and clunky forms. Our portal is backed by a serverless database to automate all site functions.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="module-grid stagger-children">
            <div class="module-card">
                <div class="module-card-img" style="background:#EEF2F6;">
                    <span style="font-size:2.5rem;">🔍</span>
                </div>
                <h3>Inspections</h3>
                <p>Custom checklist templates, Excel import, digital signatures</p>
                <a href="app/#inspection" class="module-link">Open Builder →</a>
            </div>
            <div class="module-card">
                <div class="module-card-img" style="background:#EEF2F6;">
                    <span style="font-size:2.5rem;">📋</span>
                </div>
                <h3>Legal Register</h3>
                <p>OSH compliance checklist with smart questionnaire filtering</p>
                <a href="compliance.html" class="module-link">Open Register →</a>
            </div>
            <div class="module-card">
                <div class="module-card-img" style="background:#EEF2F6;">
                    <span style="font-size:2.5rem;">🛡️</span>
                </div>
                <h3>Incident Report</h3>
                <p>Digital incident logging with staff lookup and root cause tracking</p>
                <a href="app/#incident" class="module-link">Open Form →</a>
            </div>
            <div class="module-card">
                <div class="module-card-img" style="background:#EEF2F6;">
                    <span style="font-size:2.5rem;">🧰</span>
                </div>
                <h3>First Aid & PPE</h3>
                <p>Inventory audits, shortage alerts, and stock transaction logs</p>
                <a href="app/" class="module-link">Open Console →</a>
            </div>
            <div class="module-card">
                <div class="module-card-img" style="background:#EEF2F6;">
                    <span style="font-size:2.5rem;">👷</span>
                </div>
                <h3>Contractors</h3>
                <p>Induction management, certification tracking, worker approval</p>
                <a href="app/#contractor" class="module-link">Open Console →</a>
            </div>
            <div class="module-card">
                <div class="module-card-img" style="background:#EEF2F6;">
                    <span style="font-size:2.5rem;">👥</span>
                </div>
                <h3>Staff Roster</h3>
                <p>Central personnel database with department filters and status tracking</p>
                <a href="app/#staff" class="module-link">Open Console →</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>